results.name: Irregular triangle read by rows: row n lists the numbers that can be obtained from the binary expansion of n by inserting a single 0 after any 1.
comment: All the numbers in row n have the same binary weight (A000120) as n.
xref: Cf. A000120. See A323456 for a closely related sequence, the binary analog of A323386.
results.author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, Jan 16 2019
ext: More terms from _David Consiglio, Jr._, Jan 17, 2019
